products.name: bluetooth mouse
products.description: Rechargeable Wireless Computer Mouse This USB LED wireless mouse has a built in rechargeable 500mA battery If fully charged it can be used for about 3 weeks if the battery is low the mouse light turns off and the cursor movement slows down or does not move. Please charge in time Of course this mouse also has an automatic power saving function After the mouse is powered on for 8 minutes if not in use it will enter sleep mode
